<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="release-vt">release <strong><em>vt</em></strong> ★</h1>
<p>英 /rɪ'liːs/    美 /rɪ'liːs/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>放开；松开</strong></h4>
<p>to stop holding sth (let go)：</p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Don’t release the rope.
别松开绳子。</p></div>

<h4 id="2">2.★ <strong>排放；释放</strong></h4>
<p>to let sb / sth come out of a place where they have been kept or trapped：</p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>release a prisoner 
释放囚犯</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The factory keeps releasing smoke, making the air dirty.
这座工厂不停地排放烟雾，污染了空气。</p><footer>译林⑤ – 2</footer></div>

<h4 id="3-cd">3.★ <strong>首映 (电影)；发行 (CD、书等)；发布 (新闻等) :</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>release a movie / new version 
发行影片/发布新版本</p></div></div>